### Run a pre-assessment action
POST http://127.0.0.1:8001/api/actions/pre_assess
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation_id": "<conversation_id>",
  "payload": {
    "productId": "consumer_loan",
    "segment": "personal",
    "amount": 300000
  }
}

### Run a prepayment quote action
POST http://127.0.0.1:8001/api/actions/prepay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversation_id": "<conversation_id>",
  "payload": {
    "loanId": "LN-DEMO-001"
  }
}
